            <h2>Cancellation Policy</h2>

            <p class="text-justify">Volaris Airlines provide a 24-hour cancellation policy to their passengers. This means that passengers can cancel their tickets within 24 hours of purchase. If there is any passenger who cancels the ticket 7 days before departure, they need to pay the penalty according to Voralis Airlines fare guidelines. </p>

            <h3>Refund Policy</h3>

            <p class="text-justify">To get a refund after the <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/volaris-airlines-cancellation-policy.aspx">flight cancellation</a>, the passenger has to notify the airline within 24 hours. They are eligible to get a refund without any charges only if they cancel the flight within 24 hours of booking, according to <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/volaris-airlines-refund-policy.aspx">Volaris Airlines' refund Policy</a>. </p>

            <p class="text-justify">If the flight is canceled by unavoidable situations, then the passengers will be refunded with a voucher for their future travel. They can also be refunded with the fare in their account. If the flight is canceled by regular authorities, then the airline provides the passenger with a voucher for the amount of base fare along with the additional services purchased earlier. The passenger can use that to book a new flight in the next 180 days. The airline takes 7-10 days to process the refund. </p>


