            <h3 class="text-justify">Can a passenger cancel their Volaris flight within 24 hours? </h3>
            <p class="text-justify">Yes, all the passengers have an option to cancel their Volaris flight within 24 hours. Depending on the type of ticket purchased, a passenger will have to pay some fare difference. The amount to be refunded also depends on the type of ticket. </p>

            <h3 class="text-justify">What happens if a person cancels a non-refundable ticket? </h3>

            <p class="text-justify">If a person cancels a non-refundable ticket, they must pay some fare difference. This fare difference will depend on the ticket type, length of the flight, and destination. The remaining fare is given as a credit to the passenger for future flights. </p>

            <h3 class="text-justify">How to cancel a ticket? </h3>

            <p class="text-justify">Passengers can cancel their tickets online using their mobile devices by visiting their website or app. A passenger can also cancel their flight by dialing Volaris Airline Reservations Department. Their professionals will help solve the queries. A passenger can cancel their flight ticket at the airport by visiting Volaris Airline ATO. </p>

            <h3 class="text-justify">Is the customer service center available 24 hours? </h3>

